Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,地球脉动 III
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}字幕翻译：村儿南
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是非洲中部的沙漠绿洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Guelta d'Archei in Central Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一片不毛之地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A hostile, seemingly empty world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,却孕育着生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is life here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的生命时时刻刻处于危机之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it exists at the very limits of survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是一个水资源极度缺乏的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For this is a world with almost no water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样的土地覆盖了地球上超过三分之一的面积\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lands like these cover over a third of our planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 生命被迫另辟蹊径\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here, life is forced to do things differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}第三集\N沙漠与草原
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是最古老的沙漠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the most ancient desert of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:03:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,纳米布沙漠 坐落于非洲西南部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Namib - in south west Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是地球上最热的地方之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is one of the hottest places on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管如此 这只雄性鸵鸟和它的伴侣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yet this male ostrich and his mate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,依然来到了这里组建家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}have come here to start a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很少有捕食者会在白天冒着炎热觅食\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Few predators venture out during the heat of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但这种安全是需要付出代价的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But such safety comes at a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,刚孵化出的雏鸟暴露在烈日之下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out in the open, the newly-hatched chicks are exposed to the crushing heat of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,然而有些雏鸟还没孵化出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But not all of the brood have hatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在全部孵化出来前 一家子都将留在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until they do, the family will stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,成年鸵鸟轮流负责保护雏鸟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The adults take it in turns to protect the brood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,当轮到雌鸵鸟休息时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So whilst the female takes a well-earned break,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,雄鸵鸟就会接手这项辛苦的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the male takes over for the most testing shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,它轻轻的晃动尚未破壳的蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He gently rolls the unhatched eggs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,呼唤里面的雏鸟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..calling to the young within them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,它不想落下任何一个孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He doesn't want to leave anyone behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,温度持续上升 每个小时升高5摄氏度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The temperature continues to rise by five degrees Celsius every hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,雄鸵鸟用身体挡住太阳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He protects the chicks that have emerged...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,保护刚出生的雏鸟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..shading them with his own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,经受太阳一整天的炙烤后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At the end of another gruelling day in the sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,雄鸵鸟已经精疲力竭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..he's lost almost all his energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但它必须克制住想要休息的冲动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he must resist the urge to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,凉爽的夜晚能缓解些许疲劳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The cool of the night brings some relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但同时捕食者也开始了活动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..but now predators are out and about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这将是个漫长的夜晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's going to be a long night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,黎明时分 惊喜悄然而至\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dawn brings a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,家庭增添了三名新成员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three additions to the family...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,跟刚回来的妈妈打个招呼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..to greet the returning female.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但有一个难题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在如此高温下 雏鸟很难存活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The chicks won't survive another day in these temperatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,然而雄鸵鸟并不准备离开此处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yet the male is reluctant to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,因为仍有些蛋没有孵化出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some of the eggs have still not hatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,然而时间已经所剩无几\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But time has run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,必须离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They must depart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就差了几分钟没赶上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a few minutes too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,缺少了父母的保护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alone and without the protection of its parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这只雏鸟的生存机会十分渺茫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this hatchling's chances are slim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在沙漠中生存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Survival here, as in all deserts,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,生命如履薄冰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is on a knife edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 沙漠的居民必须以非凡的方式进化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So desert dwellers have had to evolve in remarkable ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,其中有些生物成了龙与独角兽传说的源头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some have even given rise to legends of dragons and unicorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至贫瘠的沙丘也有其独到的特质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And even the dunes have their own magical quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 有些沙丘能发出属于自己的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Indeed some have their own voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在阿拉伯半岛 这种非同寻常的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here in Arabia, this extraordinary sound
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是由数十亿沙粒相互振动而产生的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is created by billions of moving sand grains vibrating against one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在这片世界上最大的沙漠中 这种诡异的旋律可以传到数里以外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The eerie song they produce can be heard for miles across the world's biggest sand desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,风也将沙子吹成了各种离奇的形状\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Winds have also built sand into surreal shapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,世界各地 如此奇异的沙漠几乎如同外星世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deserts around the world can appear so alien, that they seem to belong to another planet altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,其中最奇异的当属澳大利亚的这片沙漠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Few more so than here in Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,然而仍有一个小家伙选择了这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yet one little creature chooses this desert
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,来为它生命中最重要的环节做准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to prepare for a most important event in its life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一只雄性斑大亭鸟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A male spotted bowerbird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在过去的两个月里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the last two months,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它一直在等待短暂降雨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he has been busy in anticipation of brief rains...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只有那时 雌鸟才会寻找配偶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is when females will look for a mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,为此雄鸟搭建了一个亭台 类似一种剧院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So he's built a bower, a sort of theatre,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,如果雌鸟愿意 它们将在这个舞台上共舞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a stage on which he will dance with a female, if she is willing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,雄鸟用成堆的蜗牛壳和骨头点缀舞台入口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He decorates the entrance with piles of empty snail shells and bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没有雌性能拒绝这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How could any female resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,随时都有可能下雨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The rains are due any day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这是雄鸟改善装潢的最后机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so it's his last chance for improvements.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,蜗牛壳永远都不嫌多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can never have too many shells.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但当它离开的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But in his absence...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一只竞争对手来到此处 评估一下彼此的优劣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..a rival male drops by, to size up the competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,再搞点破坏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and cause trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,破坏对手的舞台\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wreck your neighbour's bower
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就等于完善自己的舞台\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and your own might look better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,再顺走点儿好看的装饰物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And perhaps one of the best bits would look good in his bower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,主人回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The owner is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有点儿不对劲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And something isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧时间修缮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Repairs are needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,依然没有雨水或是雌鸟的影子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still no sign of rain or females.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但它没有气馁 而是继续准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Undeterred, he continues his preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候排练求爱表演了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Time to rehearse his courtship display.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,然而遗憾的是 这只雄鸟也许永远只能独舞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But sadly he may only ever dance alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在过去的三年里 这里没有下过一场雨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the last three years, the rains have failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,而没有雨 雌鸟便不会寻找配偶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without them, the females won't mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,成立一个家庭需要雨水来提供食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They need the rains to provide food for their family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,气候的变化正在影响这些鸟类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Changes in the climate are affecting these birds,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,同时也在影响我们人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just as they are affecting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上四分之一的人口居住在干旱地区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A quarter of the world's people live in arid lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因此我们也必须应对气候的变化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we, too, have to deal with climate change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,降雨量的减少与旱期的延长使沙漠区域得以扩张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Less rainfall and extended droughts allow deserts to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,与此同时 一种自然中最令人生畏的现象之一的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And as they do, so does the likelihood
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,发生几率也大大上升\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of one of nature's most intimidating events.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,沙尘暴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A dust storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一堵近两公里高的由沙尘构筑的墙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A wall of dust up to a mile high,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,速度达到每小时110公里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}travelling at almost 70mph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如今这些破坏性风暴是有史以来最强大的风暴之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Today these destructive storms are some of the most powerful ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,势不可挡的沙尘暴穿越数千公里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unstoppable, they can travel thousands of miles...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,压垮世界各处的城镇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..overwhelming towns and cities across the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,以迅雷不及掩耳之势\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,生命需要数千年的时间才能适应沙漠的极端环境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It takes millennia for life to adapt to the extremes of deserts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这群狒狒生存于地球上最干燥的环境之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These baboons manage to survive in one of the driest environments on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,纳米比亚的埃龙戈区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Erongo region in Namibia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这里已经足有八个月没下过一滴雨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not a single drop of rain has fallen here for eight months.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这群狒狒在这里的生活十分艰难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Life here for these baboons is as hard as it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对于这只年轻的雌性狒狒来说尤为艰难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it's especially difficult for this young female.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,它刚产下第一个孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She has just given birth to her first baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,雌狒狒非常迫切的需要水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's desperate for water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没有水 它便无法产奶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without it, she can't produce milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,食物中含有的少量水分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The tiny of amount of moisture in her food
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不足以满足这对母子的需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is simply not enough for both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.12,0:21:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,狒狒群必须不断寻找水源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The troop must constantly search for water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不会为了雌狒狒停下脚步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they won't wait for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.16,0:22:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,终于 一只狒狒在岩石表面发现了一条细流\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At last, one of the troop's scouts finds a tiny trickle on a rock face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可以松一口气了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.04,0:23:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但这些水还不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But not for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻的雌狒狒只能先等待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The young mother will have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.36,0:23:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,地位决定了喝水的顺序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Access to the precious water is determined by rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,雌狒狒的地位如此之低\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is so low in the pecking order...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.76,0:23:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至可能完全喝不上水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..she might fail to get any drink at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.84,0:24:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,因为插队会受到严厉的惩罚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because jumping the queue is severely punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.72,0:24:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然风险很高 但雌狒狒不能再等了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's risky, but she can't wait any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.80,0:24:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一步险招\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A dangerous move.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.44,0:25:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但母亲的决心战胜了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there's no match for a mother's determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.72,0:25:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这些水足以保证它和孩子能坚持到下次降雨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This will be enough to keep her and her baby alive until rain falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.00,0:25:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,雨水不仅能拯救狒狒群\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rain brings salvation not just to her and the troop,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.52,0:25:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还将拯救这片干涸的大地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but to the thirsty land.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.60,0:26:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,雨水可以重塑沙漠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When it does fall, it can transform a desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.40,0:26:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,将沙漠变成地球上最富有生产力的生态系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And turn it into one of Earth's most productive landscapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.52,0:26:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,草原\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Grasslands.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.88,0:26:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,草原是地球上最大的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They support the greatest concentrations of large animals
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.88,0:26:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大型动物聚集地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to be found anywhere on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.40,0:27:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这里展现着大自然最为壮观的一面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here nature is at its most spectacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.36,0:27:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管看起来很难相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This leopardess, believe it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.60,0:27:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但这只豹子已经做好了随时启动捕猎的准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is ready to hunt at a moment's notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.20,0:27:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,它是少有的几只学会了如何隐藏在树顶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is one of the few special leopards that have learnt to hide in the tree tops,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.44,0:27:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,并等待猎物送上门来的豹子之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and wait for their prey to come to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.96,0:27:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,悄无声息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without making a sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.68,0:27:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,它已经就位了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she gets into position.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.28,0:29:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这次没能成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.12,0:29:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,现在周围所有动物都知晓它的存在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now her presence is known to all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.24,0:29:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但豹子为了成功 会付出惊人的努力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But leopards will go to astonishing lengths to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.92,0:30:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而有些豹子的胆量尤为突出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And some are more daring than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.52,0:30:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这只豹子爬到9米高的树枝上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This leopard climbs up to a branch nine metres above the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.72,0:30:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的高度比两层楼还高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's higher than the roof of a two-storey house.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.36,0:30:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,从如此高的地方跳下去很可能会危及自己的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leopards have killed themselves jumping from these heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.36,0:31:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,想要在热带草原上独当一面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To succeed on these equatorial grasslands,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.28,0:31:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就必须有着极强的适应性和过人的胆识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you must be adaptable and sometimes brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.16,0:32:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,欧亚大草原\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Eurasian Steppe,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.44,0:32:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上最大的草原\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the largest grassland on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.00,0:32:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,动物在这里接受着不同的考验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It tests animals in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.48,0:32:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的风速可以达到每小时近130公里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here, the wind can blow at speeds of nearly 80mph.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.12,0:32:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,气温可以降至零下30摄氏度以下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And temperatures drop to below minus 30 degrees Celsius.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.76,0:32:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 一种奇异的生物进化出了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yet one bizarre creature has evolved
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.52,0:32:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种极端环境下生存的方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}ways to survive in these extremes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.64,0:32:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,高鼻羚羊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Saiga antelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.48,0:33:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是一种健壮的小型动物 曾与猛犸象生活在同一个时代\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Small but tough animals that lived alongside woolly mammoths.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.04,0:33:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,雄性高鼻羚羊巨大的鼻子既能过滤灰尘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The male's enormous nose both filters out the dust
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.20,0:33:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,又能将吸入的冷空气变温暖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and warms up the cold air before it reaches his lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.08,0:33:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但每年的这个时候 鼻子还有个特别的用途\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But at this time of year, it also serves a very different purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.28,0:33:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是吸引雌性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It impresses the females.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.04,0:33:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,鼻子越大 魅力越大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the bigger it is, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.20,0:33:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这只年长的雄性高鼻羚羊知道如何吸引雌性的注意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This old male knows what it takes to hold their attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.84,0:33:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但似乎还得加把劲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But they make him work for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.12,0:34:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果收效甚微\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if that isn't effective,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.56,0:34:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那就来点别的招式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he has other ways of impressing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.40,0:34:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,头顶一从灌木 威严十足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A bush - very majestic.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.08,0:34:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,然而当你位居高位 称王称雄时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when you are king of the steppe,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.72,0:34:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,总会有挑战者虎视眈眈 觊觎你的王位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's always someone waiting to claim your crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.28,0:35:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这只年轻的高鼻羚羊认为自己可以一试\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This young buck fancies his chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.88,0:35:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它的目标是羚羊首领的眷群\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He aims to steal the king's harem.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.00,0:35:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,挑战者冲锋 准备战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The challenger charges, ready to do battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.48,0:35:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这可能会是一场殊死搏斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This could be a fight to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.64,0:35:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,发情期中的雄性羚羊有70%会失去生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}70% of rutting males will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.20,0:35:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,年长的雄羚羊最终开始占据上风\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The older male eventually begins to gain the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.84,0:36:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And with one final effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.24,0:36:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,它赶跑了这名年轻的对手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he drives the young rival away.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.72,0:36:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,羚羊群之王守住了王位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The king has kept his crown -
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.60,0:36:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,以及它的眷群\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and his harem.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.84,0:36:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,只有最强壮的高鼻羚羊才能在这片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only the strongest saigas can endure and succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.16,0:36:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上最严酷的环境之一顽强的生存下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in one of the harshest places on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.00,0:36:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,而在赤道附近 阳光和水资源得到了保障\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But close to the equator, where there is constant warmth and water,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.64,0:36:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有着天堂般的广袤草原\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there are grasslands close to paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.56,0:36:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是世界上生物多样性最丰富的草原\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the most bio-diverse grassland in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.16,0:36:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,巴西的塞拉多草原\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..the Cerrado in Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.48,0:37:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这里孕育着成千上万种独特的动植物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here there are thousands of species of both animals and plants found nowhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.56,0:37:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这个丰富多样的群落想要保持生态平衡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A rich and complex community that is kept in balance
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.48,0:37:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,便不能缺少这种幽灵般的生物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by this ghostly creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.12,0:37:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,鬃狼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A maned wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.36,0:37:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,鬃狼安静而腼腆 它们鲜为人知 较为罕见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quiet and shy, it's little known and seldom seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.96,0:37:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,与世上其他狼不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unlike any other wolf in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.76,0:37:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,鬃狼以素食为主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}their diet is mostly vegetarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.84,0:37:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,其中最受鬃狼钟爱的是狼果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they particularly like lobeira fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.72,0:38:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这种植物可以增加土壤肥力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This plant increases the fertility of the land,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.80,0:38:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,并有助于塞拉多草原的稳定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and helps to sustain the entire Cerrado.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.60,0:38:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管鬃狼看起来不像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The maned wolves, odd though it may seem,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.32,0:38:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但实际上它们是狼果这种独特植物的园丁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are, in effect, the gardeners of these unique plains.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.08,0:38:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,茂密的草丛反过来为这只雌性鬃狼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The dense grass in turn provides this female
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.36,0:38:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,提供了一个舒适的家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with a comfortable home...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.28,0:38:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,以及一个可以隐藏三只刚出生幼崽的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and somewhere to hide her three puppies,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.60,0:38:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,它们只有一个月大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just one month old.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.28,0:38:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,鬃狼过于罕见 因此这只雌性鬃狼被戴上了无线电项圈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is so rare that she's been fitted with a radio-collar
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.84,0:39:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,方便科学家进行持续的研究\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that scientists can study her continuously.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.72,0:39:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,根据我们的遥控"巢穴摄像机"显示\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And our remotely controlled "den camera" reveals a mother
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.88,0:39:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一天中 雌性鬃狼在巢穴中哺乳幼崽的时间只有数小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}only comes here for a few hours a day to suckle her pups.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.40,0:39:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,它将大部分时间都花在觅食上 以供养日益壮大的家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She spends much of her time foraging to provide for her growing family.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.60,0:39:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,此时 单独留在巢穴中的幼崽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, alone in the den,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.60,0:39:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,突然陷入了危险之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}her puppies are suddenly in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.28,0:39:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,危险并非来自于捕食者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not from other predators...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.80,0:39:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,而是来自于火灾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..but from fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.16,0:40:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,它们的家园燃起了熊熊大火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their home is being burnt all around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.28,0:40:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,火情可以在数分钟内蔓延至近两公里以外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These fires can race through a mile of grassland in a matter of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.48,0:41:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,塞拉多草原被摧毁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Cerrado devastated.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.28,0:41:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,火灾原因是什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.64,0:41:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是人类为了开垦土地种植庄稼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In order to clear land to grow crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.60,0:41:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这场大火没有波及到它们的巢穴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This particular fire didn't reach their den.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.56,0:42:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但巢穴里空空如也\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.40,0:42:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这一次 这一家子鬃狼很幸运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This time, the family were lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.52,0:42:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但整个物种正面临着令人担忧的不确定未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But her species faces an alarmingly uncertain future.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.00,0:42:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,按照目前的栖息地破坏速度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At the current rate of habitat destruction,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.96,0:42:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这些可能将是最后一批生存于野外的鬃狼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}these may be some of the last maned wolves to survive in the wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.00,0:42:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在草原上 动物与环境的联系十分紧密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In grasslands, the land and the animals
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.76,0:43:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,以至于哪怕一种关键物种灭亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are so closely interconnected, that the loss of one key species
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.36,0:43:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,都很有可能引发整个生态系统的崩溃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}could well trigger the collapse of the entire ecosystem.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.76,0:43:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这种悲剧正在非洲中部发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what happened here in central Africa,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.08,0:43:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这里足有95%的大象因象牙而被猎杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when 95% of the elephant population were killed for their ivory.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.24,0:43:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没有这些不可或缺的园丁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without these essential gardeners -
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.16,0:43:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,生命便无法繁荣生长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}life couldn't flourish.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.20,0:43:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这头雄性大象是是少数的幸存者之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This male is one of the few survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.20,0:43:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它身上依然留有过去的伤痕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He still bears the scars from his persecuted past.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.08,0:43:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但人类对象群的屠杀被及时制止了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the slaughter was stopped just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.32,0:43:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,随着偷猎行为的终止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With an end to poaching,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.84,0:44:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这头雄象成为了一个日益壮大的象群中的一份子 生活在安全之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this male is part of a growing herd that now lives in safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.36,0:44:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如今 人们认为这是最大的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Today, it's thought this is one of the largest groups
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.56,0:44:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在野外生存的非洲象群之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of African elephants surviving in the wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.48,0:44:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,随着非洲象数量的恢复\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As they recovered their numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.04,0:44:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,草原上的新苗也得以健康生长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}their grazing encouraged a healthy growth of new grasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.60,0:44:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,同时这也为其他动物创造了生存空间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they created space for other animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.48,0:44:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,让扎库马草原重获生机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..bringing life back to Zakouma.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.32,0:45:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如此奇迹般的转变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This miraculous transformation
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.00,0:45:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,表明如果大自然得以恢复平衡 生态环境将大大好转\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}shows what can happen if nature is allowed to restore its own balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.20,0:45:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,阿巴卡尔是当地护林员团队的一员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abakar is part of the team of local rangers
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.60,0:45:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们冒着生命危险保护这些大象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who risked their lives to protect these elephants.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.28,0:45:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它们视作家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see them as family
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.28,0:45:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我将这头象视如己出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think of this elephant as a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.56,0:46:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,大象不仅仅使这片土地得以复原\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the elephants didn't just heal the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.04,0:46:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还做了一件没人预料到的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They did something no-one had anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.04,0:46:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信它们已经原谅了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe they've forgiven
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.04,0:46:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,并愿意再次信任人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and trust us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.36,0:46:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,随着我们对生态系统的奇异之处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As we understand more about the wonders,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.48,0:46:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,生命彼此间的联系以及脆弱性有了更多的了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the connections and the fragility of these landscapes...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.20,0:46:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的行为造成的后果逐渐成为了人们关注的焦点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..the consequences of our actions are thrown into sharp focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.76,0:46:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这表明我们迫切需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They show we urgently need to do
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.88,0:46:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,尽一切努力帮助大自然自愈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}everything we can to help nature heal itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.88,0:47:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}幕后花絮
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.84,0:47:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,为了拍摄鬃狼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To film maned wolves,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.68,0:47:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,「地球脉动」摄制组得到了巴西先驱科学家的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Planet Earth crew joined pioneering scientists in Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.20,0:47:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,贝拉 如果你找到方向了请告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you get a direction, Bela, please let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.36,0:47:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了 大概在汽车的三点钟方向\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, she's like three o'clock from the car here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.64,0:47:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,800米远\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like 800 metres, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.36,0:47:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没有他们的帮助 我们几乎不可能追踪到鬃狼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without their help the wolves are almost impossible to track,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.64,0:47:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,更不用说在这片茂密的塞拉多草原上拍摄了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}let alone film, in the dense grass of the Cerrado.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.08,0:47:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很难找到它们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's so hard to find them,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.84,0:47:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大草原上的独居动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they're sort of solitary animals in a huge grassland
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.84,0:47:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,高达一米的草跟鬃狼一样高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with sort of metre high grass, which is the same height as the wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.72,0:47:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如同大海捞针\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it's like looking for a needle in a haystack currently.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.88,0:47:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果它要前往那个方向 我们要掉头吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shall we turn the car around, if she's going to head that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.32,0:47:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.56,0:48:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,研究人员在追踪两只戴上无线电项圈的雌性鬃狼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The researchers have radio collared two female wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.24,0:48:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,两只狼都哺育有幼崽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Both have puppies.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.20,0:48:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们希望能追踪一只狼到它的巢穴 并在里面安装远程摄像头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They hope to track one to a den and set up remote cameras inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.88,0:48:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,得到的录像将为研究人员提供重要信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The footage would provide the researchers with crucial information
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.64,0:48:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,并有助于保护这种濒危物种\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and help to protect this endangered species.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.04,0:48:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,它就在这附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's in here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.28,0:48:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,鬃狼太特别了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maned wolf, they're so special.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.72,0:48:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,更多地去了解这个物种非常重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's very important to understand more of this species.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.84,0:48:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,越是了解 就越能保护到它们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When we get more knowledge, its getting easier to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.84,0:48:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,然而其中一只雌性鬃狼的信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the signal from one of the females
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.96,0:48:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,将他们带向了一个令人担忧的方向\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}takes them in a worrying direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.76,0:48:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,信号指向这片规模巨大的农田\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it's led us directly into this huge epic scale farmland,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.08,0:48:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说 我从没见过这么大规模的农田\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the likes of which, to be honest, I've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.16,0:48:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这表明鬃狼的自然栖息地已经寥寥无几\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it shows you what little is left of their natural habitat.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.12,0:49:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,50%的鬃狼栖息地变成了农田\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}50% of maned wolf habitat has been lost to farmland.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.20,0:49:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,无线电项圈显示它们常常误入这片陌生的土地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the radio collars show they now regularly stray into this unfamiliar landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.52,0:49:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不幸的是 研究人员在农田中发现了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tragically, the researchers discover the body
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.92,0:49:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,戴有项圈的雌性鬃狼的尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of one collared mother wolf on farmland.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.84,0:49:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,它的死因不明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The cause of her death unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.60,0:49:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,而它的幼崽将难以独自存活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her puppies won't survive alone for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.40,0:49:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,事不宜迟 研究人员动身寻找幼狼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without delay, the researchers set out to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.46,0:49:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,鬃狼幼崽在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The puppies are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.60,0:49:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们救出了五只一个月大的幼狼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They rescue five, one-month-old pups,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.44,0:49:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它们藏在草丛中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hidden in the long grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.20,0:49:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们尽快出发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's get going
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.60,0:49:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这些幼崽难以承受炎热的阳光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the puppies can't cope with the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.80,0:50:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为了评估幼狼的身体情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To assess their condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.48,0:50:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,它们被送往急救机构\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the pups are taken to an emergency rescue facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.64,0:50:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,它脱水很严重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's very dehydrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.60,0:50:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,它们将受到全天候的照顾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They will be cared for around the clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.28,0:50:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,直到它们足够强壮 可以回归野外为止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until they are strong enough to be released back into the wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.84,0:50:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,鬃狼妈妈的死亡对每个人来说都是巨大的打击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their mothers death is a huge blow for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.28,0:50:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对于摄制组来说 拍摄鬃狼巢穴仅剩的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the crew, the only chance of filming in a den
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.36,0:50:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是另一只戴有项圈的雌狼 名为诺琳尼娅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}now lies with one remaining collared female known as Nhorinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.40,0:50:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,它在更右边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's more here to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.44,0:50:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那是它吗 不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that her there? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.04,0:51:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到它了 就在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yep, I can see her, she's there. She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.36,0:51:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了 找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, got her, got her, got her.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.96,0:51:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,它在往两点钟方向走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's coming towards two o'clock now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.80,0:51:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,离汽车50米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}50 metres away from the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.28,0:51:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,它正从树后过来 我们等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's coming behind this tree in the middle here, let's wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.48,0:51:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了 看到它了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got her, I've got her. OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.28,0:51:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,最终 摄制组拍到了诺琳尼娅的第一张照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eventually the team capture the first images of Nhorinha on camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.28,0:51:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,终于看到我们要找的鬃狼了 太神奇了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To finally see our wolf is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.60,0:51:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,借助无人机摄像头 摄制组跟踪到了它的巢穴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Using a drone camera, they follow her to her den.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.68,0:51:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,无人机首次拍到了诺琳尼娅的幼崽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The drone reveals the first glimpse of Nhorinha's puppies.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.72,0:51:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.52,0:51:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,诺琳尼娅在挪动幼崽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And she's moving them...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.52,0:52:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的举动是第一次被见证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..something that's never been witnessed before.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.92,0:52:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这太特别了 我的心都停止跳动了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is very special, my heart stopped there, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.92,0:52:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢相信我真的在见证这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't believe what I'm really seeing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.48,0:52:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在知道巢穴的位置了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We know where the den is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.28,0:52:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天早晨 摄制组再次来到巢穴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The following morning, they return to the den site.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.28,0:52:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想安装摄像头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They want to rig their cameras,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.36,0:52:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但只能在确认诺琳尼娅不在巢穴后才能安装\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but can only approach when they know Nhorinha is not at the den.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.64,0:52:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,它在附近吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is she nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.24,0:52:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,还没收到信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no signal yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.84,0:52:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,诺琳尼娅在一公里之外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nhorinha is out of here, at least 1km.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.76,0:52:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对我们来说是个好消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it's very good news for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.68,0:52:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,试着靠近巢穴吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's try to approach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.04,0:52:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,芭芭拉确认了诺琳尼娅离这里很远\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Barbara checks that Nhorinha is away from the den,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.40,0:53:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,因此摄制组可以在不打扰它的情况下进入巢穴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so the team can go in without disturbing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.68,0:53:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.68,0:53:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这个巢穴并不明显\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The den isn't immediately obvious,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.28,0:53:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但这里没有草丛遮蔽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the grass here is flattened,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.04,0:53:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因此他们安装了摄像头 并希望一切顺利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so they place their cameras and hope for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.52,0:53:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们大概离巢穴80米远\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're about 80m from the den.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.44,0:53:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在确保安全的前提下 这已经是最近的距离了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is as close as we can be safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.16,0:53:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是关键时刻 开启摄像头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the moment of truth, we're turning them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.88,0:53:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,拍到巢穴的实况了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we're live,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.60,0:53:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,摄像头位置没变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the camera hasn't moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.08,0:53:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,卢克负责守着摄像机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Luke keeps watch over the cameras,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.92,0:53:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,团队其他人则继续监视诺琳尼娅的动向\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}while the team continue to monitor Nhorinha's movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.64,0:53:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没过多久 他们便停下了脚步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Before long, they are stopped in their tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.20,0:53:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,只见远处冒出滚滚黑烟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just see this huge plume of smoke in the distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.04,0:53:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就在鬃狼一家子的巢穴后面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you know, directly behind the den where our mother maned wolf has been with her puppies.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.40,0:54:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我很着急 其他研究人员肯定也是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm quite anxious. I'm sure the other researchers are as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.68,0:54:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很可能是农民放的火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the fire may well have been started by farmers,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.96,0:54:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,为了开垦土地种植庄稼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in order to clear land to grow crops
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.64,0:54:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,用于喂养养殖的鸡和牛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that will be used to feed chicken and cattle around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.96,0:54:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们作业的地点离大火很近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The heat from the fire when we're working that close
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.32,0:54:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,以至于我的手臂能感觉到有火在烤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is so intense that I can feel it burning the skin on my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.16,0:54:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,大火蔓延速度特别快 根本逃不开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It moves so fast, there's no way you'd escape something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.68,0:54:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,全身上下的每个细胞都想赶紧逃离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every single cell in your body just wants to get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.40,0:54:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但实际上这整片区域\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But actually this whole place,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.96,0:54:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,整片塞拉多草原 是被农田和公路包围着的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this whole Cerrado, is surrounded by farmland and roads,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.28,0:54:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果仔细想一想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so, actually, when you really think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.40,0:54:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,野生动物根本无处可逃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the wildlife has nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.56,0:54:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,芭芭拉以及整个研究团队度过了艰难的几周\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After a difficult few weeks for Barbara and the research team...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.40,0:55:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好吗 情况如何 -挺好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello, how you doing? How was it? It was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.60,0:55:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,摄制组带来了些好消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The crew have some good news for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.84,0:55:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有一只\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, track, there's one right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.56,0:55:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right now. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.48,0:55:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-你能看到吗 -这是实况吗 -是实况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you see? That's live? Yeah, yeah, that's live.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.60,0:55:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.12,0:55:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没见过这么可爱的小家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never see anything so cute in my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.72,0:55:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我也从来没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! Me neither. Me neither, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.32,0:55:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧它正盯着摄像头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at this! Look, it's looking at the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.96,0:55:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.04,0:55:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是世上第一次在鬃狼巢穴内\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the first record in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.72,0:55:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如此近距离记录幼狼的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so intimate inside the den.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.88,0:55:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,从来没人见过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody ever saw this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.80,0:55:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如此重要物种的新信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Such new information of such important species.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.52,0:55:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你也很激动吗 芭芭拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You feeling emotional, Barbara?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.44,0:55:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很难不激动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's difficult not to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.64,0:55:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,难以用语言描述\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have words to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.52,0:55:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这对我来说太重要了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's too much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.16,0:56:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,摄像头继续拍摄前所未有的镜头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The cameras continue to gather first-of-its-kind footage,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.48,0:56:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,帮助人们深入了解鬃狼生命中极为重要的最初几周\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}providing insight into the all-important first weeks of a maned wolf's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.96,0:56:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,以及至关重要的 帮助我们认识到为一代代生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, crucially, how much space must be protected
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.44,0:56:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,保护自然生态的重要性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to support future generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.12,0:56:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我衷心希望世上每个人都能看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I really hope that every person in the world could see
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.00,0:56:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这些动物是多么特别 多么美好 多么神奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from their house, how special, and how beautiful, amazing these animals are.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.52,0:56:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我感到十分担忧 但并没有绝望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel quite worried, but not hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.00,0:56:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我会奋战每一天来帮助这些动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will fight every day and every year to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.40,0:56:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我生在这片草原 长在这片草原\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was born in Cerrado, I grew up in Cerrado,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.40,0:56:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,塞拉多草原是我的家 我必须保护她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and Cerrado, it's my home, I have to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.32,0:57:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,下一集\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.80,0:57:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,淡水世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..the world of freshwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.72,0:57:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,地球的命脉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The lifeblood of Planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.96,0:57:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,动物非凡卓绝的精彩戏码在这里拉开帷幕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And a stage for the most extraordinary animal dramas.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.92,0:57:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,「栖息地探索者」生动地展现动物和它们的栖息地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Habitat Explorer brings animals and their habitats to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.76,0:57:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,探索这个免费互动程序并制作折纸动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Explore this free interactive and make origami animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.16,0:57:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,前往bbc.co.uk/planetearth3\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to bbc.co.uk/planetearth3
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.68,0:57:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,点击链接进入开放大学\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and follow the links to the Open University.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.76,0:57:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,或者订购免费印刷版\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or to order a free printed version,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.92,0:57:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎访问网站或拨打屏幕上的号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}visit the website or call the numbers on the screen.

